{"version":1,"content":"<html><body><p>鑽石山龍蟠苑發生火警。今日（5日）早上約11時26分，龍湖閣低層一單位起火，驚動多人報案，有人一度報稱需要求助；消防接報趕抵救援，11時51分將火</p><p>現場可見，起火單位火光熊熊，冒出大量濃煙；約100人自行疏散，幸無釀傷亡。警方及消防經初步調查後，相信涉事單位廚房抽氣扇短路，並無可疑。</p><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260505/1128303344922660864427135.jpeg/jp_9an5aUk8rBUKEWoWyuyg3T5uZ2XExWcpRe3DKUXs\" alt=\"鑽石山龍蟠苑龍湖閣一單位起火，冒出濃煙。（讀者提供）\"><figcaption>鑽石山龍蟠苑龍湖閣一單位起火，冒出濃煙。（讀者提供）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260505/1128320477194883072296318.jpeg/QbmHNV1_4PRnHJK1CnYfrr2THaQTRwzox0hvmu5Ib5o\" alt=\"逾百居民疏散。（馬耀文攝）\"><figcaption>逾百居民疏散。（馬耀文攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260505/1128320479673847808283754.jpeg/GctxSWm6f84GwIhTcji6XnAm9GiHBjAGd9cFW17XBVs\" alt=\"警方及消防接報趕抵。（馬耀文攝）\"><figcaption>警方及消防接報趕抵。（馬耀文攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260505/1128320482358333440546290.jpeg/hHs7LNnBMV3Xcsjdc3j3bZNOJuRT__8UEZ05czidOXM\" alt=\"逾百居民疏散。（馬耀文攝）\"><figcaption>逾百居民疏散。（馬耀文攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260505/1128320484774383616351209.jpeg/bN3muN2Flo9riK5D_HzYu5Y8u2LrzKQ-e8qrtVLKq7U\" alt=\"消防趕抵救援。（馬耀文攝）\"><figcaption>消防趕抵救援。（馬耀文攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260505/1128320487098159104587913.jpeg/EOhALii1ny4jpb7P00vy4EeHVYpEA5rQX8QrRHbEK0Q\" alt=\"現場為鑽石山龍蟠苑龍瑚閣。（馬耀文攝）\"><figcaption>現場為鑽石山龍蟠苑龍瑚閣。（馬耀文攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260505/1128320477073248256291758.jpeg/PuVhF_fEvF172vjaekzUeIzFCeFm3pDNXvIPhHfyD4Q\" alt=\"鑽石山龍蟠苑龍瑚閣一單位起火，事後外牆明顯熏黑。（馬耀文攝）\"><figcaption>鑽石山龍蟠苑龍瑚閣一單位起火，事後外牆明顯熏黑。（馬耀文攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260505/1128320479518658560273954.jpeg/n8Pb1X81QiM-zP-_GK0g78cw9K22xOsK9Wxa9txsWvY\" alt=\"消防趕抵救援。（馬耀文攝）\"><figcaption>消防趕抵救援。（馬耀文攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260505/1128320482039566336891306.jpeg/7OpPmoHa06tIVnWJnELTsQl1M_TGr7veMc4wdRjOMHU\" alt=\"鑽石山龍蟠苑龍瑚閣一單位起火，事後外牆明顯熏黑。（馬耀文攝）\"><figcaption>鑽石山龍蟠苑龍瑚閣一單位起火，事後外牆明顯熏黑。（馬耀文攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260505/1128320484430450688598713.jpeg/IIS5_5ngs92nBi2hs5N_GefeP0rXyJUY-PNWjtHzVo4\" alt=\"鑽石山龍蟠苑龍瑚閣一單位起火，事後外牆明顯熏黑。（馬耀文攝）\"><figcaption>鑽石山龍蟠苑龍瑚閣一單位起火，事後外牆明顯熏黑。（馬耀文攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260505/1128301910340669440276051.jpeg/XlY6WYbsHO_7EMuM40KvYI11LvzHpsXcqPDyrIHw8qw\" alt=\"鑽石山龍蟠苑龍湖閣一單位起火，火光熊熊。（讀者提供）\"><figcaption>鑽石山龍蟠苑龍湖閣一單位起火，火光熊熊。（讀者提供）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260505/1128301657969397760802673.jpeg/e6yIZ4YaWGea-9K0_ZZtHvGR-SC-QBhTaMS9SWjEvUk\" alt=\"鑽石山龍蟠苑龍湖閣一單起火，濃煙沖天。（Threads / 3d.ownmsil）\"><figcaption>鑽石山龍蟠苑龍湖閣一單起火，濃煙沖天。（Threads / 3d.ownmsil）</figcaption></figure></body></html>","scraped_at":"2026-05-05T05:57:09.193156+00:00","quality":{"score":1,"chars":424,"images":12,"source":"HK01 突發","fallback":"none"}}